OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening. Then the rest of
OL,7,Fthe night will be dry with clear
OL,8,Fperiods and just the odd shower. Cold
OL,9,Fwith patchy frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FThe morning will be dry.
OL,12,FRain will spread east across all parts
OL,13,Fduring the afternoon and evening.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain at
OL,16,Ffirst on Friday then drier with a few
OL,17,Fshowers. Cloudy on Saturday with rain,
OL,18,Foccasionally heavy, spreading east.
OL,19,FCold and bright on Sunday with
OL,20,Fshowers. Severe gales possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
